[`case int32`](/documentation/coreml/mlmultiarraydatatype/int32)Designates the multiarray’s elements as 32-bit integers.[`case float16`](/documentation/coreml/mlmultiarraydatatype/float16)Designates the multiarray’s elements as 16-bit floats.[`case float32`](/documentation/coreml/mlmultiarraydatatype/float32)Designates the multiarray’s elements as 32-bit floats.[`case double`](/documentation/coreml/mlmultiarraydatatype/double)Designates the multiarray’s elements as doubles.[`static var float: MLMultiArrayDataType`](/documentation/coreml/mlmultiarraydatatype/float)Designates the multiarray’s elements as floats.[`static var float64: MLMultiArrayDataType`](/documentation/coreml/mlmultiarraydatatype/float64)Designates the multiarray’s elements as 64-bit floats.
